hat is linked to a horrific tragedy of any kind,\\\" Hadid wrote in a statement to her Instagram Story on Monday.\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Instagram Story\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any art\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"a horrific tragedy\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"Hadid\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued, \\\"In advance of the campaign's release, I had no knowledge of the historical connection to the atrocious events in 1972.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign's release\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"no knowledge\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"the historical connection\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"the atrocious events\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am shocked, I am upset, and I am disappointed in the lack of sensitivity that went into this campaign.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"sensitivity\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"this campaign\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Had I been made aware, from the bottom of my heart, I would never have participated.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My team should have known, adidas should have known and I should have done more research so that I too would have known and understood, and spoken up.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My team\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"adidas\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"more research\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As I always have, and always will, speak up for what I believe to be wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid noted that the intentions of all parties involved were \\\"to make something positive, and bring people together through art\\\" but said that the lack of understanding of the 1972 tragedy \\\"undermined\\\" their efforts.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hadid\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"the intentions\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"all parties\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"understanding\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1972 tragedy\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"their efforts\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Further into her statement, Hadid emphasized that she is a proud Palestinian woman and that the country \\\"is not synonymous with terrorism.\\\"\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9999998700709596, \"rank\": 1.21995387769443e-07, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://d